data.title: PASSPORT SERVICES — EMBASSY OF THE REPUBLIC OF TUNISIA
data.meta_site_name: EMBASSY OF THE REPUBLIC OF TUNISIA
data.text:
Copy of Tunisian Birth Certificate (Must Register the Birth first, ONCE you complete the registration THEN apply for The Passport “Application link “)

We will not accept both applications at the same time. ( Application will be rejected ).

Two copies of Tunisian ID Card C.I.N ( if lost, damaged, expired, or over the age of 18 and never had an ID please fill up the C.I.N Pledge form )

Two Copies of The Tunisian ID Card C.I.N ( if lost, damaged, or expired or over the age of 18 and never had one please fill up the C.I.N Pledge form )

Two Copies of US Permanent Resident Card, US Passport, or proof of legal status in the USA.

(Pending Green card cases, will require a copy of the USCIS receipt notice)*
